{"tid":369216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【刑不上支那】建設銀行職員行賄罪成，判200小時服務令","createTime":"2017-08-22T07:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T07:15:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e279f1a4cdb0e1bbf7c7ebf5b7765064eb4ce8","tid":369216,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170822/large/1503372990_8aaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170822%2Flarge%2F1503372990_8aaf.jpg&h=fe04b0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170822/57111904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170822%2F57111904&d=X6Djyr7Uwvr%2FHWJcRpc4ZPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=0cfc2659\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170822%2F57111904&h=febb6401\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170822/57111904</a><br />\n<br />\n建設銀行前銷售經理夥同下屬，向一名營業額未達標的營業代表索取6,000元，以換取給予對方「救命單」令對方達標。營業代表拒絕後被要求辭職，廉署接報揭發事件。經理及下屬被控串謀索賄罪，早前受審後罪成，法官今於判刑時指案情嚴重，但考慮被告背景和報告良好，各判處200小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被告銷售經理周凱聰（33歲）及營業代表郭偉倫（28歲）的代表律師均指二人已受深刻教訓，難再從事銀行業，他們的社會服務令報告內容正面。郭的大律師指郭沒有利用職權犯案，沒有侵害銀行和申請借貸的客戶的利益，屬特殊情況求免除監禁。"},{"pid":"17cc244259197cf038901004a5cd6596f70af573","tid":369216,"uid":17510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行賄都係得200個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話係刑事罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b2bae7910f892fd6eb000603f6b9835a334b44","tid":369216,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets